data.description: This stunning five bed, four bath home includes a newly-remodeled kitchen, featuring granite countertops and stainless steel appliances; opens right up to a bright living room and well appointed fireplace. There is a large loft over the spacious attached three-car garage with a bathroom and more than enough room for an office and a bedroom, or a guest room for company. The primary suite includes a lovely five-piece bath with all new counter tops. This large home and property also features a main-floor laundry room, a large, finished walk-out basement with wet bar and a bedroom. The upgrades don’t stop there! Outside this beautiful home are two large outbuildings. The largest 3000-square foot shop includes two 12-foot doors, four livestock pens with water and open up to a large pasture. It also has concrete floors and electricity. The second shop expands 2500 square feet and is a full concrete floor. All of this and more in a great location, just minutes from town! Don’t miss your opportunity to own this beautiful 16 + acre estate!
